Class RDF2Vec

  • java.lang.Object
    • RDF2Vec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRDF2Vec

    public class RDF2Vec
extends Object
implements IRDF2Vec
    This class allows to generate walks and train embeddings for RDF2Vec Classic.
